The official diaspora* project account. Follow us to receive all the latest news about updates and events!
**Talk to us** - diaspora*: @mention this account to ping us - Join our [mailing list](http://groups.google.com/group/diaspora-dev) to contact us by email - IRC: #diaspora or #diaspora-dev on irc.freenode.net - [Github](https://github.com/diaspora/diaspora) to signal bugs and participate to the code - [Loomio](https://www.loomio.org/groups/194) to take decision with the community
**Official blog** http://blog.diasporafoundation.org/
